<h1>About The List</h1>

<p>This app is developed by Creative Commons.</p>

<p>Through The List, organizations will provide lists of locations,
people, and events that they need photographs of. And when users are
in the right place at the right time, they can claim an item from the
list and publish a photograph of it.</p>
	
